# Finance Dashboard using Power BI

## Project Overview

This project showcases an interactive Power BI dashboard developed to analyze loan application data and provide business insights. The dashboard helps track loan approvals, applicant risk levels, and key performance indicators (KPIs) for better decision-making.

## Objectives

* Visualize loan application data
* Monitor approval and rejection trends
* Analyze applicant risk categories
* Support data-driven business decisions
* Create interactive reports and dashboards

## Tools Used

* Power BI
* Microsoft Excel
* Data Visualization Techniques

## Dashboard Features

* Loan Approval Analysis
* Risk Category Distribution
* Approval vs Rejection Trends
* KPI Monitoring
* Interactive Filters and Slicers
* Business Performance Insights

