## Key Insights

* Identified approval and rejection patterns
* Analyzed applicant risk distribution
* Monitored important lending KPIs
* Improved reporting efficiency through visualization

## Business Benefits

* Faster reporting
* Better decision-making
* Improved data visibility
* Enhanced business intelligence capabilities

## Skills Demonstrated

